h2 Meetings
p Meetings are held at 19:00, every last Thursday of the month, at the #{link_to 'Electron Club', 'http://www.electronclub.org/doku.php'}.  Check out our past meetings, whatâ€™s on this month, and what might be coming up on our #{link_to 'meetings', meetings_path} page.
