p Our IRC channel, #{link_to '#scotlug', 'https://webchat.freenode.net/?randomnick=1&channels=%23scotlug&prompt=1'}, is usually busy and helpful.  There is a #{link_to 'mailing list', 'http://mailman.lug.org.uk/mailman/listinfo/scottish'} for general announcements.
